Revision history for Perinci-Sub-DepChecker

0.11    2015-09-03 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

	- [dist] Move spec prereqs from RuntimeRequires to
	  DevelopRecommends to reduce deps but still allow indicating spec
	  requirement.


0.10	 2014-05-28 (SHARYANTO)

         - Implement pkg & func (Rinci 1.1.48).


0.09	 2013-11-20 (SHARYANTO)

         - No functional changes. Add 'use experimental smartmatch' for perl
           5.18+.


0.08	 2012-12-06 (SHARYANTO)

         - No functional changes.

         - dep 'prog': Show PATH in error message.


0.07	 2012-08-09 (SHARYANTO)

         [ENHANCEMENTS]

         - Load Perinci::Sub::Dep::* automatically on unknown dep.


0.06	 2012-06-07 (SHARYANTO)

         - Update to Rinci 1.1.18 (remove 'undo_storage' clause, add 'tmp_dir',
           'trash_dir', 'undo_trash_dir').


0.05	 2012-05-02 (SHARYANTO)

         [ENHANCEMENTS]

         - Support 'prog' clause (new in Rinci 1.1.14), old 'exec' clause is
           still supported for backward compatibility.

         - Add utility functions: dep_satisfy_rel() and
           list_mentioned_dep_clauses()


0.04	 2012-02-10 (SHARYANTO)

	 - Rename distribution from Sub-Spec-DepChecker to
	   Perinci-Sub-DepChecker. Move Perinci-/Perl-specific dependency types
	   to Perinci.


0.03     2012-01-25 (SHARYANTO)

         - Add missing dep to File::Which (thanks Andreas Koenig, RT)


0.02     2012-01-20 (SHARYANTO)

         - No functional changes. Mark deprecation.


0.01     2011-08-31 (SHARYANTO)

         - First release.
